{"TopicId":172584,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"The Real Solar System Visual Enhancements topic is closed to further replies","CreatedByName":"MaltYebisu","CreatedById":186157,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-18T09:06:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MaltYebisu","CreatedById":186157,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-18T09:06:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1570104875\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/153511-122-real-solar-system-visual-enhancements-v122-rc4-2017-09-03/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022146521\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Phineas Freak\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s forum topic for the\u00A0Real Solar System Visual Enhancements mod seems to be locked with the message \u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#c75050;font-size:13px;\u0022\u003EThis topic is now closed to further replies\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u0022 displayed where you would usually type a reply at the bottom of the page. I could not find a post by a moderator telling that the topic was closed. Instead, it looks to me like the topic was locked mid-conversation when \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/2795-softweir/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00222795\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/2795-softweir/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@softweir\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0explained to a user that you need\u00A0to upload files to a file-sharing service to be able to link them in a post.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf this locking of the topic is deliberate, then it would be nice to see a short message from one of the moderators explaining that the topic is closed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgba(220,220,220,.498039);background-image:url(\u0026quot;%7B___base_url___%7D/applications/core/interface/ckeditor/ckeditor/plugins/widget/images/handle.png\u0026quot;);\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure if this is the right forum for this or if this belongs in Kerbal Network. If it\u0027s wrong, please move it and forgive me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T23:16:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe request may have come through here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7513856572\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129807-need-your-own-thread-moved-or-locked-post-here/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:192px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaltYebisu","CreatedById":186157,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-23T12:21:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223330531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172584\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521674174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/22/2018 at 12:16 AM, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe request may have come through here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3230236009\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129807-need-your-own-thread-moved-or-locked-post-here/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:189px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you, \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI checked, but I couldn\u0027t find a recent request from \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022146521\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Phineas Freak\u003C/a\u003E. The last post in the RSSVE topic is from March 4th, and I couldn\u0027t see anything related to that topic in the recent posts in the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129807-need-your-own-thread-moved-or-locked-post-here/\u0026amp;page=45\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Emove or lock topic\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-24T09:22:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223332073\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172584\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521807696\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022186157\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaltYebisu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, MaltYebisu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you, \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI checked, but I couldn\u0027t find a recent request from \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022146521\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Phineas Freak\u003C/a\u003E. The last post in the RSSVE topic is from March 4th, and I couldn\u0027t see anything related to that topic in the recent posts in the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129807-need-your-own-thread-moved-or-locked-post-here/\u0026amp;page=45\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Emove or lock topic\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI saw this as soon as it happened.\u00A0 In doing some research (stalking) the mod author wanted it temporarily closed, but the forum moderators were reluctant to close, reopen threads ad infinitum and the mod author said that they would statr a new thread in the future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have three guesses as to why (you could PM them and ask, or they might see this topic and enlighten us)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThey have no interest at this time to keep updating the mod, but may return.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u00A0The mod works fine, but people cannot read nor follow instructions and the author wanted a break.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMy favourite conspiracy (you heard it here first !) Squad/ T2/ whoever was going to do exactly the same thing - stock sized real solar system - as part of/ update date to MHE or a future DLC pack and asked the mod to be removed for a time while they established it.\u00A0 I reckon that once the bugs are ironed out of Making History, Squad will release Earth/ Moon/ planets and major moons in stock size, because this is what history is all about - or it will be a $5 addon but with axial tilt.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nOne can only dream.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaltYebisu","CreatedById":186157,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-29T17:34:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122369\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@theJesuit\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf \u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022146521\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/146521-phineas-freak/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Phineas Freak\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0wanted it closed, then everything is fine. I was worried that some mistake had been made and just gone unnoticed.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wish the moderator that closed the topic would indicate that in a post to avoid confusion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}